openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Fruits
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /add/path:
    get:
      operationId: getAddPath
      parameters:
        - name: fruit
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            pattern: apple|banana
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: query parameter fruit'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
